snippet.title: beatmania 3rdMIX (Arcade / 1998) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
beatmania 3rdMIX, emulated via MAME 0.182 (using the new PortAudio output module).  I really like nouvo nude.

0:50 Quadra - life goes on "AMBIENT"
2:43 nouvo nude - wild I/O "HOUSE"
4:32 ESPACIO BROTHERS - METALGEAR SOLID ～Main Theme "BIGBEAT MIX"
6:41 DJ FX - Attack the music "HARD TECHNO"
8:51 nouvo nude - find out "SOUL"
10:38 staccato two-F - La Bossanova de Fabienne "BOSSA GROOVE"
12:45 Crunky Boy featuring Muhammad - Queen's Jamaica "REGGAE"
14:34 nouvo nude - super highway "drum'n bass"
16:44 Credits
